  <section>
    <h1>General Component Tips</h1>

    <ul>
      <li>Always call 'this._super(...arguments)'</li>
      <li>
        Always clean up after yourself
        <ul>
          <li>Remove/Tear Down events, listeners, and plugins</li>
          <li>Try to make your didInsertElement and willDestroyElement mirror opposites</li>
          <li>Use template actions whenever possible</li>
          <li>Favor Ember native addons and events over jQuery or vanilla libraries</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>Mind the Prototype</li>
      <li>Implement your feature at the right component context</li>
      <li>
        Keep your Component easy to reason about
        <ul>
          <li>Stick to and use to the Lifecycle</li>
          <li>Render the data/state consistently (functional)</li>
          <li>Pass as much data as possible in (DDAU)</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>

  </section>

